Description: Elaboration of fix emissions inventories,
    consisting in four stages, pre-processing activity data, preparing 
    emissions factors, estimating the emissions and post-processing of emissions 
    in maps and databases. More details in  <doi:>.
    Before using FEIN you need to know the industrial composition of your study area, in other words,
    the combination of industrial type, size and fuel of the fleet. Then, it is recommended to
    start with the project to download a template to create a structure of directories and scripts.
